Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you ever experience it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Two shockingly beautiful eyes{/eyes - didn't wanna use the same word twice in a row, especially since in Japanese this is two different words for eyes}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,A startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over {(not really sure about what the original meaning should be)}{L-E's variant: As she spreads that kind heart - Perevodildo}{With her gentle heart, winning everyone over }
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,Whose winning heart lavishes kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for our \NRomantic Era High Collar Lady to leave the nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as her fate takes a new, unexpected turn. {運命の歯車, a figurative meaning expression in Japanese, not sure about how I could put it better}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She indeed has to learn the ways of marriage, \Nas required by etiquette,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and now nobody can stop her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but now she'll have to face a warrior in the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is just a dream, it's definitely a bad one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the shogunal vassal's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stall, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pomp coming with a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's for the promotion of a new doll. {Idk, I took the italian version, I don't understand the sentence in japanese: お人形の(?)の(?)なんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this seem like a decoration to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts just to look at...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the shogunal vassal's daughter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an enemy of the emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going back to the days \Nof Meiji Restoration now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels pretty anachronistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're a woman, I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You butcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:03.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,500)\c&HEEE5E4&\pos(720,180)\bord0\blur1.5\b1\fs}Episode 7\N{\fs100}Count, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, relax! I am a good guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,975,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You butcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this Boss calling out for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to calm down, you damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to skewer you! \NStop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What else am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I trust this strict count.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is now being taught to be ladylike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't expect her to be very dedicated. {/will not exercise enough} {運動不足になっておるかもしれんのう, I don't know if he means this in a positive or a negative way}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, my goal was to raise hell and get kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had a katana, \Nhe wouldn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had a katana... Katana, katana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just this, I'll cut the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If that hits me by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll end up murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "Milord" right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, could she be referring to this mansion's landlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I doubt so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, only princes, \Ncounts and barons get called that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't suppose this is the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that there could be a count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As mad as it sounds, this stuffed samurai doll is... {Boys' May Festival dolls stuffed toy; stuffed animal; plush toy; soft toy; cuddly toy} {/Gatchaman}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he is Count Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am Shinobu's grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that this guy is a count?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That girl is out of her mind, treating me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To be fair, it was your own doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what in the world were you trying to do, \Ndressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll never allow a marriage \Nwith the daughter of a shogunal vassal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no clue that he is a count...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry too,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he is a genuinely good man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's a little headstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"A little headtsrong" is quite the understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, you didn't get injured, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, that's enough! Shut up and listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,won't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's a prince or a count,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he was still trying to murder one of his guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything ever happens to Boss Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what this goldfish tattoo truly means! {he's referring to the tattoo in some way, but I don't understand the second half, he's surely threatening her though}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadja say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you saying to ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just an oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, why are you making such a racket \Nwith your rickshaw over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of our sight right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming here, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly resemble your grandfather, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thick eyebrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,your stiff lips,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all of your masculine features.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Masculine features?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This stings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, my long-time love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rapid flow of water{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}may get split in two by a stepping stone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it will eventually turn into one again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be finally fulfilled, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the day we marry ever come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Ah! Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I'm afraid of dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou isn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so hard to understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boys, you can listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you are protecting the people who live here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou is trying his best to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They have never been affectionate to strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be a big thorn in the flesh!{I don't understand this, he says こうしゃくな something something}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, this is surely a strange feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something incredible just happened:\NBenio tamed Tenmaru and Chimaru with no trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get along with her, you two. {unsure of the meaning of わかる here}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like dogs are way smarter \Nthan people here, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Boss Benio while I'm not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I'll go away at once, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ushigorou? He's my hen-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. He is my-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Lady Benio's devoted manservant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm sure I heard him say "Boss".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to make it short,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in Benio's family they use\Nthis word instead of the usual "Sir," grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, knowing you, I didn't expect your coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This get-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again snickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I bet you've already caused some mischief,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret I wasn't there watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I am not an Asakusa spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see that you two are already \Nin such a playful mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, do not add to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is such a grandmother's good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be because she brought him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that he respects elders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope he's independent too. {not too sure about this last part}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, Ms. Kisaragi is going to assist you \Nall the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her to me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the count is from Kagoshima, \Nwe follow those traditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's difficult, but please get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to teach her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with great attention until the wedding day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood curdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, please show Lady Benio her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so your grandfather is from Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've already met him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that old-fashioned madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, he's not a bad person,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he's just a little stubborn and proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's way too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've died in a matter of minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...he just wanted to intimidate you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he resent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to like \Nthat your ancestors were shogunal vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Meiji Restoration, \Nthey and the Satsuma Domain fought to the bitter end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they were both Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened moons ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's inappropriate to fuss over it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, please calm down, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit that even I didn't behave properly at all, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can picture this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, just stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to sum it up, after your grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,bade farewell to my grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she met and married your grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a samurai from Satsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,since they had a son and your grandparents too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,their promise fell on grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are the chosen ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less, but don't mind about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's now on the Ijuuin family's bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't jump to conclusions yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They are still not officially married yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, why are you so battered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two enormous lupine dogs attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Benio? She didn't get injured, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It ended in a blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, even though they shredded my clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment they saw Boss, \Nthey became docile in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,even the Ijuuins could become
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as affectionate to her very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio went there to try to break her betrothal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm doubtful about the viability of this plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny could be already written.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful... It's just like a foreign princess's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's like a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that I'm thinking, all of a sudden? {/what the dickens}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a great panorama from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired, so I'll take leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is a marvelous room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate both Shinbou and this house, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I only like my new room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need to get changed only to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our mores, so follow them and dress up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't- want to- just- let me- go-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tough, but we made it with style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just because you forced me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving now, I'd love a good dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll eat all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and lick the leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Western style? I don't know these manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know these manners...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever our High Collar Lady goes,\Nit turns into a symphony of laughter and romance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny has many things in store!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady, not knowing western manners
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is catapulted into a clanking table.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being on the verge of tears,{Idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind Shinobu gave her a glimpse of a sweet dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,incessantly disrupted by her table mates!{I don't understand}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Benio going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Here Comes the High Collar Lady:\NI won't weep 'til I win! Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me a High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me once again this loving glance{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have this unrequited feeling{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
